results.title: Cottage Chic Quilted Mug Rug in Peach, Coral and Mint  - Mini Quilt, Ready to Ship
results.description:
This mini quilt is peachy keen!  With gorgeous floral prints in peach, mint and cream, this is a true celebration of spring!  It would be a delightful gift or a wonderful treat for yourself!

If you have never bought a mug rug, they are smaller than a placemat, but larger than a coaster.  I make mine identical to a real quilt, only so much smaller!  :) The uses for these are endless!!!!  How about on the coffee table to set the remote control and a cup of tea?  By your bed to set your phone or medication on?  Anywhere you need to protect a table, under a vase, plant, or the phone in the kitchen.  The best part is, they are SO pretty.  It is like having a mini quilt on your table, in any color you wish.  I think they are more fun than doilies! 

The top layer of this is made using high quality quilter's cotton cut and pieced into a fabric "checkerboard", there is cotton batting in the center and a white muslin fabric on the bottom.  I machine quilted and attached a binding I made out of matching peachy rose fabric.  This measures approximately 8 1/4 x 10".

This item is finished and is ready to ship to you.  All items are designed, cut and pieced by me in my smoke free home.  I prewash all my fabric in a mild, fragrance free soap.  

Try spot cleaning, but if necessary, you may machine wash this on a warm, gentle cycle and dry on low.  This is a miniature quilt, so it will pucker when laundered.  Touch up with hot iron.  Enjoy!

Please remember colors may vary from monitor to monitor.  This listing is for one mug rug only.  Phot props are not included.

Thanks for visiting!
